steps.html_instructions: Turn right to stay on Maruf Köyü Yolu
Merge onto Ankara Çevre Yolu/O-20 via the ramp to İstanbul/Eskişehir/E88

Exit onto Eskişehir Yolu/D200/E90 toward Polatlı/Eskişehir/İzmir
Continue to follow D200/E90
Take the ramp to Afyon Ankara Yolu/D260/E96

Exit onto Eskişehir Konya Yolu/D675
Continue to follow D675
Take the exit toward Konya Denizli Yolu
Keep right at the fork and merge onto Afyon Keçiborlu Yolu/D650
Take the exit toward Afyon Denizli Yolu/D320
At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto Yeni Denizli Cd./D320

At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto Afyon Denizli Yolu/D320
Continue to follow D320
Turn left at the 1st cross street onto Denizli Muğla Yolu/D585/E87
Take the exit toward Denizli Muğla Yolu/D330

Continue onto Denizli Muğla Yolu/D330
Continue to follow D330
At the roundabout, take the 1st exit onto Uğur Mumcu Blv.
At the roundabout, take the 1st exit and stay on Uğur Mumcu Blv.
At the roundabout, continue straight onto Cumhuriyet Cd.
At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto Recai Güreli Cd.
